data.description: CHARMING COWESETT COLONIAL  WELCOME TO THIS INVITING COLONIAL STYLE 2,670 SQ FT OF LIVING SPACE, 4 BED, 2.5 BATH HOME NESTLED IN THE SOUGHT-AFTER AREA OF COWESETT, IN WARWICK, RI, NEIGHBORING EAST GREENWICH, MINUTES AWAY FROM THE WATERFRONT, FINE DINING, AND SHOPPING. JUST TEN MINUTES FROM T.F. GREEN INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT AND AMTRAK. BE GREETED BY A SPACIOUS LIVING AREA WITH PLENTY OF WINDOWS AND LIGHT. A GAS BURNING FIREPLACE FOR ENJOYMENT. THE EAT-IN KITCHEN IS GREAT FOR ENTERTAINING AND HOSTS A BREAKFAST NOOK STYLE BENCH WITH A MOVEABLE ISLAND WITH STORAGE. COUNTERTOPS ARE GRANITE AND ALL APPLIANCES ARE STAINLESS STEEL. THERE ARE PLENTY OF CABINETS WITH EASY CLOSE DRAWERS AND A DEEP KITCHEN SINK LOOKING OUT TO THE PRIVATE SUNNY BACKYARD RETREAT. OFF THE KITCHEN IS A LAUNDRY AREA WITH A HALF BATH. AROUND THE CORNER YOU WILL FIND A COZY FAMILY AREA DECORATED WITH SHELVES AND A WOOD BURNING FIREPLACE. A BONUS TO THIS CHARMING HOME, A FOUR-SEASON SUNROOM THAT LOOKS OUT AT THE BACKYARD AND CAN BE USED FOR GATHERINGS, THEATER ROOM, STUDIO OR OFFICE. THE UPSTAIRS OFFERS/HOSTS 4 BEDROOMS, ONE MASTER WITH FULL BATH AND AN ADDITIONAL FULL BATH ON THIS LEVEL TO ACCOMMODATE ALL SCHEDULES. THIS HOME IS LOCATED IN A PRIME LOCATION, OFFERING PEACE AND CONVENIENCE. MAKE THIS HOME YOURS! WITH A LITTLE TLC, THIS IS YOUR DREAM HOME COME TRUE.
